Entries.default: "A basket, sir? To carry all sorts of things."
Entries.female: "A basket, miss? To carry all sorts of things."

Entries.default: "We open our arms to you, and you slay our kin! Leave this place!"
"I say Clario will place blame on Ikawha for the death of this Rinco. Mokeha is foolish."
"For what do you do this?! Leave us in peace!"
"Ekera, Hylea sends us many storms this season."
"Other tribes never visit us. You came from very far?"
